Cell.Text: G|I see. Then please leave my tower.

[S] G|The package is something I've been seeking for some time. | I can't give too many details - I sparsely know much myself, actually. | I have heard whispers of relic: one that wields considerable power. | I've grown weary about allowing things of a magical nature being allowed to rot in the dark places of the world. | I have hired countless adventurer's to retrieve this relic for me, and none have seemed to return. | Head over to the tavern here in Morthal. I've heard there's some adventurer's in town seeking something of the description...
Well, I suppose if you're offering, I could use your help.

Node.Caption: JT_AuxentiusPackageQuest3: Maybe I can help you find what you're looking for?

Cell.Text: So you're not the messenger then. Do you make it a habit to waste people's time?

Node.Caption: JT_AuxentiusPackageQuest2: Uh, what was it you were expecting again?

Cell.Text: Well? Where is it? Hand it over!
Yes, yes. Are you the messenger? Did you bring the package?

Node.Caption: JT_AuxentiusPackageQuest_Thalondir0Topic: You're not from Morthal are you?

Cell.Text: None of your business, lad. Now leave me be.
